name: arachnos_soldier
display_help:
Not recommended for new players. Can't access the tutorial. Must start as a Villain.

Begin your career as Wolf Spider with a strong mix of Melee and Ranged attacks and strong protective powers available via your power armor. Beginning at level 24, you may choose to progress down the "Crab Spider" or "Bane Spider" path. Crab Spiders gain access to the "backpack" and the powerful claw/cone attacks it provides, while the Bane Spider track provides stealth and a stronger focus on melee.
